com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.checks

Class Check

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.checks.Check

  • public class Check
extends java.lang.Object
    The type Check. It's responsible of filtering out the matches by processing the check operations. Resulting matches are the ones for which a report should be filed.
